    public class TestSparseRowStore
extends ProxyTestCase<IIndexManager>
implements IRowStoreConstants
    Test suite for SparseRowStore.

    Note: A lot of the pragmatic tests are being done by the BigdataFileSystem which uses the SparseRowStore for its file metadata index.

      • test_timestampSemantics

        public void test_timestampSemantics()
        Test the semantics of timestamps associated with property values by atomic row writes.

        Each row write is assigned a timestamp and the property values written in that atomic operation all get the assigned timestamp. The same value may be overwritten and the new version is always the one with the most current timestamp.
